WEBVTT

00:12:58.292 --> 00:13:01.684
We just need to cultivate
the conditions together.

00:13:01.708 --> 00:13:03.559
We need each other.

00:13:03.583 --> 00:13:05.434
To support each other

00:13:05.458 --> 00:13:08.434
and allow ourselves to really meet this.

00:13:08.458 --> 00:13:10.292
That's what we need, so ...

00:13:11.625 --> 00:13:13.250
Let's take a deep breath.

00:13:15.333 --> 00:13:17.559
Have compassion for ourselves

00:13:17.583 --> 00:13:20.976
and one another in this moment,
time in history,

00:13:21.000 --> 00:13:24.893
so we collectively process
these painful truths,

00:13:24.917 --> 00:13:26.875
these difficult realities.

00:13:28.333 --> 00:13:29.875
Let's do this together.